        {
            "title": "加密貨幣總市值蒸發逾1萬億美元 比特幣觸及7個月低點",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 幣圈動盪周三進入新階段，比特幣跌至七個月低點，推動加密貨幣總市值蒸發超過1萬億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">比特幣在紐約交易時段一度跌至88,522美元，最新一輪暴跌波及從散戶「抄底族」到數字資產財務公司等各類投資者。而在周三晚些時候輝達發布強勁營收展望、緩解市場對全球AI支出熱潮可能降溫的擔憂後，代幣價格自低位反彈。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">下一個心理關口位於85,000美元和80,000美元附近。加密貨幣總市值在10月6日達到約4.3萬億美元峰值，目前徘徊在3.2萬億美元附近。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6ce5110e-4432-313a-af57-4350f9e030e3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/V.i119zOCWNQg2PpV9VGcw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/df3a2dfb52880f90de442f6d6c6e3857\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Crypto World Wipes Out $1 Trillion as Bitcoin Plunges Anew</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86%E8%B2%A8%E5%B9%A3%E7%B8%BD%E5%B8%82%E5%80%BC%E8%92%B8%E7%99%BC%E9%80%BE1%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B9%A3%E8%A7%B8%E5%8F%8A7%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E4%BD%8E%E9%BB%9E-225211982.html",
