        {
            "title": "人工智能教父之一LeCun將最早於本周宣布離開Meta",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"人工智能教父之一LeCun將最早於本周宣布離開Meta\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/oZ62PqVatghZK0Hne5FQAQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/ca42af20-c5ac-11f0-b757-ffdff3e2db61\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">人工智能教父之一LeCun將最早於本周宣布離開Meta</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
